  "title": "Sales Executive (Indoor\\Outdoor)",
  "description": "<p><strong>*IMMEDIATE START*</strong></p><p>Seeking showroom consultants for established bathroom and kitchen distributor</p><p>-This position is located at <strong>Commonwealth and/or Marina Square</strong></p><p>-Main responsibilities include assisting in showroom sales to <strong>high-value customers </strong>including interior designers and architects as well as landed home owners</p><p>-Must be comfortable producing quotations for interior designers, architects and project owners</p><p>-This position has base salary + incentive scheme</p><p>-This is a challenging position with several paths to grow including into management</p><p>-Relevant experience will determine base salary</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>-A good attitude and dependability is key for this position.</p><p>-<strong>Experience in interior design or renovation is a big plus</strong></p><p>-Company is willing to train and support if candidate is keen to learn and develop</p><p>-Decent English (conversational) is required</p><p>-Neat appearance is expected</p><p>-Necessary to work on the weekends and some PH (2 days off / 1 day off per week on alternate weeks)</p><p><br /></p><p>We encourage all applicants regardless of age or experience, and value diversity.<br />Work-sharing can be considered.</p>",
